        <description>Two widely used extension of WordPress contains pretty severe errors. Unfortunately not every security hole can be fixed.
Researchers at High-Tech Bridge in the previous weeks two WordPress plugins started to monitor closely. They did a thorough security analysis in the case of TheCartPress plugin which is made to support e-commerce and WP Photo Album Plus which is an extension especially for photo management. In both of them they found risky vulnerabilities, despite the latter received the proper fixes.</description>
        
